{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/so/MyWorkSpace/personal/care-inomi/.worktrees/feature/initial-setup","sessionId":"b2eaba6d-901e-4124-895a-44aab4df41c1","version":"2.1.19","gitBranch":"develop","agentId":"aedfc84","slug":"giggly-watching-meteor","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"Implement BaseLayout.astro for the Astro project.\n\nWorking directory: /Users/so/MyWorkSpace/personal/care-inomi/.worktrees/feature/initial-setup\n\nCreate src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro with the following structure:\n\n```astro\n---\nimport \"../styles/global.css\";\n\ninterface Props {\n  title: string;\n  description: string;\n  ogImage?: string;\n  noIndex?: boolean;\n}\n\nconst { title, description, ogImage, noIndex = false } = Astro.props;\nconst canonicalUrl = new URL(Astro.url.pathname, Astro.site);\nconst ogImageUrl = ogImage ? new URL(ogImage, Astro.site).href : undefined;\n---\n\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/svg+xml\" href=\"/favicon.svg\" />\n    \n    <!-- SEO Meta Tags -->\n    <title>{title}</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content={description} />\n    <link rel=\"canonical\" href={canonicalUrl} />\n    {noIndex && <meta name=\"robots\" content=\"noindex, nofollow\" />}\n    \n    <!-- Open Graph -->\n    <meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\n    <meta property=\"og:url\" content={canonicalUrl} />\n    <meta property=\"og:title\" content={title} />\n    <meta property=\"og:description\" content={description} />\n    {ogImageUrl && <meta property=\"og:image\" content={ogImageUrl} />}\n    <meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"ja_JP\" />\n    <meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"合同会社あいのみ\" />\n    \n    <!-- Twitter Card -->\n    <meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" />\n    <meta name=\"twitter:title\" content={title} />\n    <meta name=\"twitter:description\" content={description} />\n    {ogImageUrl && <meta name=\"twitter:image\" content={ogImageUrl} />}\n  </head>\n  <body class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col bg-white text-neutral-800\">\n    <!-- Header will be added later -->\n    \n    <main class=\"flex-1\">\n      <slot />\n    </main>\n    \n    <!-- Footer will be added later -->\n  </body>\n</html>\n```\n\nAlso update astro.config.mjs to add the site URL:\n\n```javascript\n// @ts-check\nimport { defineConfig } from 'astro/config';\nimport react from '@astrojs/react';\nimport tailwindcss from '@tailwindcss/vite';\n\nexport default defineConfig({\n  site: 'https://ainomi.co.jp',\n  integrations: [react()],\n  vite: {\n    plugins: [tailwindcss()]\n  }\n});\n```\n\nUse the Write tool and Edit tool."},"uuid":"aca3074f-57e9-45d7-9de4-939dae7ebfc8","timestamp":"2026-01-25T15:28:09.226Z"}
